OL,3,C'Depraved' man hid in homes to
OL,4,Csecretly film people having sex
OL,6,FA man who entered people's homes
OL,7,Fwithout permission to secretly film
OL,8,Fthem naked, including having sex, has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed for a total of eight years.
OL,11,FThe victims of Kirk Geoff Bishop, 40,
OL,12,Ffilled the public gallery at
OL,13,FGuernsey's Royal Court to hear how he
OL,14,Frecorded and saved more than 100
OL,15,Fvideos and images of them, without
OL,16,Ftheir consent, in intimate situations.
OL,18,FHe also stole underwear and filmed
OL,19,Funder a woman's skirt outside of a
OL,20,Fshop.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
