PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778893392
OL,3,C'Depraved' man hid in homes to
OL,4,Csecretly film people having sex
OL,6,FHis crimes spanned several years and
OL,7,Fwere only discovered after a couple
OL,8,Fcaught him in their house.
OL,10,FIn sentencing for the most serious
OL,11,Foffences, Judge Russell Finch called
OL,12,Fwhat Bishop did "wicked and depraved".
OL,14,FHe added, "In 52 years as a judge in
OL,15,Fthe UK and Guernsey, I can only
OL,16,Frecollect two similar cases, neither
OL,17,Fof this scale."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
