FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778893392
OL,3,C'Depraved' man hid in homes to
OL,4,Csecretly film people having sex
OL,6,FThe 40-year-old had pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fall 17 charges, including trespass
OL,8,Fwith intent to commit a sexual
OL,9,Foffence, voyeurism, and burglary.
OL,11,FBishop committed the offences between
OL,12,F2022 and 2025 against 14 people across
OL,13,Fthe island.
OL,15,FHe was caught on 16 September last
OL,16,Fyear when a couple came home from
OL,17,Fplaying sport and found him in their
OL,18,Fbedroom, with their adult sex toy
OL,19,Fswitched on on the bed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
