PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778893392
OL,3,C'Depraved' man hid in homes to
OL,4,Csecretly film people having sex
OL,6,FBishop was chased out of the house and
OL,7,Fapprehended in the street, with the
OL,8,Ffollowing police investigation
OL,9,Fdiscovering two phones containing
OL,10,Fvoyeuristic videos which identified
OL,11,Fsome of his other victims.
OL,13,FThey include a woman who had
OL,14,Fpreviously reported to the police that
OL,15,Fsomeone had been filming her in her
OL,16,Fown home after she got out of the
OL,17,Fshower.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
