FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778893392
OL,3,C'Depraved' man hid in homes to
OL,4,Csecretly film people having sex
OL,6,FThe court heard how officers arrested
OL,7,Fand held the wrong person for three
OL,8,Fdays, with the case then dropped due
OL,9,Fto a lack of evidence, before Bishop's
OL,10,Fphone revealed it to be him.
OL,12,FVictims also shared with the court the
OL,13,Fserious impact these intrusions have
OL,14,Fhad on their lives.
OL,16,FOne said, "The whole incident has
OL,17,Fterrified me. I feel violated, I
OL,18,Fshould feel safe in my home but I
OL,19,Fdon't."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
