FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778893392
OL,3,C'Depraved' man hid in homes to
OL,4,Csecretly film people having sex
OL,6,FAnother explained, "I live in a
OL,7,Fpermanent state of high alert."
OL,9,FIn a letter submitted to the court,
OL,10,FBishop admitted, "I am ashamed of
OL,11,Fmyself. It was like something had come
OL,12,Fover me."
OL,14,FHis defence stated that there was no
OL,15,Fsharing of images and the 40-year-old
OL,16,Fsuffers from depression, as well as
OL,17,FADHD which they said explained his
OL,18,Flack of impulse control.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
