FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778893392
OL,3,C'Depraved' man hid in homes to
OL,4,Csecretly film people having sex
OL,6,FThey added that Bishop's partner has
OL,7,Fstood by him throughout the legal
OL,8,Fprocess.
OL,10,FAlongside his eight-year jail
OL,11,Fsentence, Bishop will be placed on the
OL,12,Fsex offenders' register for a decade
OL,13,Fand face strict conditions for five
OL,14,Fyears after he is released.
OL,16,FThese include a night curfew and being
OL,17,Fbanned from owning a camera without
OL,18,Fpermission.
OL,20,FMore crime news:
